Class MappedSequences<T>

  • Object
    • MappedSequences<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassLiterals, PackageLiterals

    public class MappedSequences<T>
extends Object
    A multimap from keys of type T to sequences. Such a map can be useful to specify sequences that should only be used in specific contexts, for example sequences that should only be used as components when testing a specific class.
